These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, october, june
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, fanta
1. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
3. the person drinking water is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Birthday   | june | february | october |
| Beverage    | milk    | fanta | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, handball, biathlon
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, begonia
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who growsaconite is the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Sport       | handball | biathlon | water-polo |
| Flower   | begonia    | aconite     | iris        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, aconite, zinnia
3 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, dog
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Flower         | zinnia     | aconite | begonia |
| Pet   | bird | lizard     | dog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
City: miami, prague, london
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, blue
1. the person traveling to prague is the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person traveling to miami is the person who likes blue##1
3. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| City   | london | prague  | miami  |
| Color         | purple  | fuchsia | blue |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, 7up
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, july, june
1. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage         | iced-tea   | 7up | sprite    |
| Birthday   | july | june     | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different games are played: chess, bridge, mah-jongg
3 different pets are kept: turtle, frog, fish
1. the person playing chess is the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the fish is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game   | bridge | mah-jongg | chess   |
| Pet   | fish     | turtle    | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, police-officer, mechanic
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, sudoku, baking
1. the police-officer is on the right of the accountant##1
2. the accountant is between the person who's hobby is baking and the mechanic##2
3. the accountant is on the left of the police-officer##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Job   | mechanic | accountant | police-officer |
| Hobby           | sudoku         | skydiving         | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, golf, handball
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, metal, indie
1. the fan of ambient is between the fan of metal and the person who's sport is tennis##2
2. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Sport   | golf | handball | tennis |
| Music-Genre    | metal    | ambient | indie     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, disaster, adventure
1. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing   | puzzles  | hiking  |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure | disaster | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, surfing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, family, crime
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport   | volleyball    | surfing      | water-polo |
| Movie-Genre       | family | crime | western   |

