2. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Sport         | handball | cricket | swimming |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy   | sports |

