.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, amber, black
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, bellflower
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who likes mauve is the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
4. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Color   | black | amber | mauve |
| Flower     | aconite     | iris   | bellflower        |

