.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, roller, car
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, musician, paramedic
1. the person driving the car is between the person driving the roller and the musician##2
2. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
3. the musician is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Transport   | roller | car | train |
| Job     | analyst    | paramedic  | musician   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
City: marseilles, venice, miami
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, mouse
1. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
4. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| City   | marseilles  | miami     | venice |
| Pet   | pony | chinchilla | mouse    |

