.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
House: townhouse, colonial, tower
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, swisher, dannemann
1. the dannemann-smoker is the tower house##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| House          | tower | townhouse | colonial  |
| Cigar   | dannemann      | vegafina  | swisher |

