.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, weightlifting, skiing
3 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, mah-jongg
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Sport   | snowboarding | skiing | weightlifting    |
| Game           | backgammon     | mah-jongg  | scrabble |

