.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, designer, software-developer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, cricket, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the firefighter##1
2. the firefighter is in the middle##1
3. the software-developer is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job         | software-developer | firefighter   | designer |
| Sport   | cricket   | water-polo | tennis      |

