.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, blood-red, grey
House: gothic-revival, wooden, cottage
1. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
2. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Color      | blue | blood-red | grey |
| House   | wooden   | cottage          | gothic-revival |

