.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, november, january
City: liverpool, london, prague
1. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Birthday     | november  | january   | march |
| City   | prague | london | liverpool       |

 